<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>280</hymn_number>
<title>HMAI AH KAL CH280</title>
<key>Db</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa na Pathian zum in, Hmaiah kal, hmaiah kal, A bia fek te'n i
 tlaih in, Hmai ah kal, A minthiang kha hlaw hin hlah, Ning-zahnak a si
 hmanh ah, A min thannak kha chim in, Hmai ah kal.

[V2]
 Riantuan awkah an au maw? Hmaiah kal, hmaiah kal, Atu Amah riantuan
 tuah, Hmai ah kal, Zumhnak le dawtnak fonh in, Amah kha i bochan tuah, A
 dongh tiang fek te'n dir in, Hmai ah kal.

[V3]
 Amah nih thlaici an pek, Hmai ah kal, hmaiah kal. Tuh law na zun than
 hna lai, Hmai ah kal, Na Bawipa kuttang ah khan, Hngah in um zungzal ko
 tuah, Na thlacamnak a theih lai, Hmai ah kal.

[V4]
 A donghnak kha a nai cang, Hmai ah kal, hmaiah kal. A rian kha tuan
 zungzal law, Hmai ah kal, Khrih cu na vo, na nunnak, Vancung changreu kha
 a si, Sunparnak ni na phan lai, Hmai ah kal.</lyrics>
</song>